	codes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue reserves the right to cha
	nge delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have a tic
	ket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no elevator. Stairs and
	 ramps only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. A
	rrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing 
	ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by email if assist
	ance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us
	 at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless 
	freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and their compani
	ons. Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator to the balcony 
